text: Paula Westher (born 16 April 1965) is a Swedish former cyclist. She competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Sweden Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Malmö
